{"tid":902924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(全港淪陷) 長者周日免費乘港鐵新渡輪","createTime":"2018-11-15T07:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T10:26:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1abf507d8114030863887082e6eb34299cae6a13","tid":902924,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"【晴報專訊】下周日（18日）為「長者日2018」，65歲以上的長者只要使用長者八達通，可免費乘搭港鐵、輕鐵及港鐵巴士，其八達通將不會被扣除車費，但優惠不適用於機場快綫、往來羅湖及落馬洲站的車程，東鐵綫頭等亦須支付附加費。新渡輪亦表示，當天長者只需出示由香港社會福利署發出之「長者咭」，即可免費乘搭中環至長洲、梅窩及北角至紅磡、九龍城的普通渡輪普通客位，但不適用於豪華客位及高速船。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E4%B9%98%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%96%B0%E6%B8%A1%E8%BC%AA-225033859.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E4%25B9%2598%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E8%25BC%25AA-225033859.html&d=GxiPe3%2BoLEteQwn1b8MQp5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8d27238b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E4%B9%98%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%96%B0%E6%B8%A1%E8%BC%AA-225033859.html</a>"},{"pid":"f11a96e8cff862cfcdb57a3f219f250224d15dd5","tid":902924,"uid":102096,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac478d1f43235c4c3188b4b5031a96b549a0fe8f","tid":902924,"uid":40750,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"星期日求奇啦"},{"pid":"dad22633694efd3e106b1588d74fa853607d259c","tid":902924,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:21:41.000Z","msg":"又玩鳩香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ce3faed28720b4019a8203c3602a5c4733f917","tid":902924,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T07:23:19.00